{"tid":1630427,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"小心走入人民鬥人民困境！！！！","createTime":"2019-10-06T12:28:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T12:37:24.000Z","uid":85390,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f56fe94fd9c1d35037b983bf473b29c8957501b8","tid":1630427,"uid":85390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:28:23.000Z","msg":"我個人好支持獅鳥出手打人/傷人嘅藍絲，同埋幫福建幫鋪頭裝修。<br />\n<br />\n但請大家記住，唔好因爲無哂目標而將門檻降低，隨便行事，咁樣只會同對家一樣。至少至少我地有嘅仍然係道德。<br />\n<br />\n對準政權，癱瘓政府機構，禍及狗屋同狗仔女，呢啲更加係主要應該做嘅野，唔好因爲困難而唔做。隨便係街打政見唔同嘅人或裝修政見唔同嘅鋪頭，呢啲可能好易做到，但最後只會陷入人民鬥人民嘅局面，所以要小心。<br />\n<br />\n出師有名，行之有理。光復香港，時代革命！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"934f25937d90aad5a8b4ee6424932686de2ede72","tid":1630427,"uid":303304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:29:03.000Z","msg":"大家知唔知道宜家外國人點諗勇武<br />\n勇武要大家backup 啊！<br />\n<br />\n正式宣布：文宣洗地開始［行動po求置頂］<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630198\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630198</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f799770bd4ed8e671904bc752b17b4d0f5173abe","tid":1630427,"uid":12412,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:29:21.000Z","msg":"你以為你唔打人哋唔打你？醒下啦"},{"pid":"122393c021e97f31a79b5253d0a6c46afe3597ee","tid":1630427,"uid":85390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f799770bd4ed8e671904bc752b17b4d0f5173abe","tid":1630427,"uid":12412,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:29:21.000Z","msg":"你以為你唔打人哋唔打你？醒下啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:30:09.000Z","msg":"自己睇下我打啲咩再講"},{"pid":"3de8a3fc296db6d373f5723ee48d895aa95bcd71","tid":1630427,"uid":85390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:31:20.000Z","msg":"唔好為滿足自己而將門檻降低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f25e81b17dd17f9fa5761901353c